nd the network. </p>\n<p>In this talk, we learn how to use Fresco and build a demo app to show how images can be progressively shown on the device.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Scalable Image Management with Fresco on Android","date":"Jan 01, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/talks/2021/scalable-image-management-with-fresco/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/talks/2021/testing-svelte-with-jest/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Testing Svelte with Jest: Validate Your Components Quickly!"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/talks/2021/mobile-debugging-with-flipper/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Mobile Debugging Made Easy with Flipper"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2125292342","2915660680","3649515864","63159454"]}